# Patched tmux-256color terminfo with undercurl (Smulx) and underline
# color (Setulc) support. macOS ships ancient ncurses that lacks these
# capabilities, so Neovim inside tmux won't render undercurl without this.
#
# Compile with: /usr/bin/tic -x <this-file>
tmux-256color|tmux with 256 colors,
	use=tmux-256color,
	Smulx=\E[4:%p1%dm,
	Setulc=\E[58::2::%p1%{65536}%/%d::%p1%{256}%/%{255}%&%d::%p1%{255}%&%d%;m,
